Package org.tmotte.tmplz.util

Useful classes that didn't fit in anywhere else.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ObjectFormatter
    A convenience interface that allows one to intercept Objects passed to Section.fillin() and format them.
    TemplateInterceptor
    This can be assigned to a TemplateManager so that one can do any necessary manipulations to a template before it is released for use, or just prior to rendering.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Log
    For internal use.
